title: #137: Care What You Wear (@KevinGChristy, @NickYoussef)
itunes:title: Care What You Wear with Kevin Christy, Nick Youssef
description: Kevin Christy had Nick Youssef and me over to his house to talk about what I need to change with my wardrobe. Kevin and Nick have always been my fashion advisors and we used it as an excuse to do a fun little podcast. In honor of fashion week (probably) (somewhere) I present to you a guide to what to wear as a man in late 2013.
